headline: Here Are My Top 5 Nasdaq Stock to Buy in 2025
summary: The Nasdaq Composite (NASDAQINDEX: ^IXIC) has been a great performing index, as it beat the broader S&P 500 (SNPINDEX: ^GSPC) in 2024 by rising 28.6% versus the S&P 500's 23.3%.  It wouldn't surprise me to see those results again in 2025, but I think a few companies within the Nasdaq Composite can outperform the broader index in 2025.
